‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ web/                    # Next.js frontend
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packages/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ solver/                 # Python solver
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ shared/                 # Shared TypeScript types
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ db/                     # Database schema & migrations
